like that, John.

03:12.777 --> 03:14.779
<i>You okay here?
Yeah. Yeah. Yeah.</i>

03:18.908 --> 03:21.578
- It stinks really bad.
<i>- She.</i>

03:21.786 --> 03:23.288
She stinks really bad.

03:23.496 --> 03:25.957
She does smell for a woman.

03:26.166 --> 03:27.542
Wish someone
had found her sooner.

03:27.750 --> 03:28.835
Leg.

03:30.295 --> 03:31.504
Turn your head.

03:32.338 --> 03:36.176
Oh, Ron's getting lazier.
He didn't even clean her.

03:36.384 --> 03:39.179
He just declared natural causes
and shipped her over.

03:39.387 --> 03:40.388
Other leg.

03:56.237 --> 03:57.947
<i>Aneurysm hooks.</i>

